com.uber.crumb.annotations - package com.uber.crumb.annotations
 
com.uber.crumb.annotations.internal - package com.uber.crumb.annotations.internal
 
CrumbConsumable - Annotation Type in com.uber.crumb.annotations
A convenience annotation that can be used to indicate that this type should be available to the Crumb processor and any of its extensions (since processors have to declare which annotations they support).
CrumbConsumer - Annotation Type in com.uber.crumb.annotations
Annotation to indicate that a given class should consumer crumb metadata from the classpath during processing.
CrumbIndex - Annotation Type in com.uber.crumb.annotations.internal
An annotation for recording information about a given index in crumb.
CrumbProducer - Annotation Type in com.uber.crumb.annotations
Annotation to indicate that a given class should produce crumb metadata from the classpath during processing.
CrumbQualifier - Annotation Type in com.uber.crumb.annotations
This annotation can be used on custom other annotations to indicate that they are relevant for Crumb and given to extensions in their APIs.
